WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.680
You have already seen where you can rate the crew members you work with in my jobs after the job is completed,

2
00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:09.360
but did you know you can give them an overall rating as well?

3
00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:14.080
Simply click on Network on your home screen and search for the crew member you want to rate.

4
00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:18.720
Click on the star rating under their name and select Write a review.

5
00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:22.200
You can give them up to five stars and write a comment.

6
00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.960
Click on Submit and you are done.

7
00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:28.480
Ratings help the member grow and earn more money.

8
00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:37.200
Remember, others can rate you too, so always arrive on time, finish on time, and do quality work.

9
00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:40.000
You can also connect with crew members here.

10
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:43.440
Click Contact member to send a message.

11
00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:49.760
You can connect with crew members that you prefer to work with and invite them to join jobs you are on.

12
00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:55.600
Networking helps you learn, grow, earn more, and connect with other trusted members.